{
  "stem": "22944.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No schooling, but we lived there for a little while, till actually, the decree came that all the Jews have to be-- must assemble somewhere.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they will have to be evacuated from the town, or deported.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do remember that decree very much-- very strongly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my late father went to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, he had to keep us, somehow, going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never been to his workplace, but I believe it was on other side of the river.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a panic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I do not know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My sister, Edith, must have found out that something is going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because she went out to investigate this terrible panic in town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she sort of-- through another newspaper, and telephone, and if the radio was on-- we didn't have a radio, anyway-- what was going on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So firsthand information was only to go out and find out yourself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So she went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And sort of decree came that all the Jews have to be-- assemble now and have to be taken away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And by 6:00, there will be curfew-- no Jews allowed to be in the street anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember my father went to work, Edith went out to look what's going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother, and my sister Gertie and me went out to look for our father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we went till the river.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was a little bridge and two men standing there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my mother said that she would like to go to look for my father, I presume.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And these men also said, we don't advise you to go across the river.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It will be difficult to come back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think they gave us some kind of hint.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
